- @page_title = 'Cookies Policy'
.content
  %h2 How we use Cookies

  %p Cookies are very small text files that are stored on your computer when you visit some websites. 

  %p We use cookies to help identify your computer so we can tailor your user experience, track shopping basket contents and remember where you are in the order process.

  %p You can disable any cookies already stored on your computer, but these may stop our website from functioning properly.

  %p The following is strictly necessary in the operation of our website.

  %p This Website Will:

  %ul
    %li Remember what is in your shopping basket
    %li Remember where you are in the order process
    %li Remember that you are logged in and that your session is secure.  You need to be logged in to complete an order.
    %li The following are not Strictly Necessary, but are required to provide you with the best user experience and also to tell us which pages you find most interesting (anonymously).

  %h2 Functional Cookies

  %p This Website Will:

  %ul
    %li Offer Live Chat Support (If available)
    %li Track the pages you visits via Google Analytics
    %li Targeting Cookies

  %p This Website Will:

  %ul
    %li Allow you to share pages with social networks such as Facebook (If available)
    %li Allow you to share pages via Add This (If available)
    %li To view the ‘Add This’ Privacy Policy or to opt out of any online behavioural advertising, please visit Add This and click on the ‘Opt Out’ button.

  %p This website will not

  %ul
    %li Share any personal information with third parties.